SqlScript:
Use sufs

SELECT HM.FirstName, HM.LastName, S.GradeLevelID
FROM dbo.Household H
JOIN dbo.Application A ON H.ApplicationID = A.ApplicationID
JOIN dbo.HouseholdMember HM ON HM.HouseholdID = H.HouseholdID
JOIN dbo.Student S ON HM.HouseholdMemberID = S.HouseholdMemberID
WHERE H.ApplicationID = $[FTC-OLA_ApplicationID] 

AND HM.FirstName = '$[FTC-OLA_StudentFirstName]' 

AND HM.LastName = '$[FTC-OLA_StudentLastName]'
Name: FTC-OLA_ValidateApplicationStudent
